Name: ulcmNsStandardEvent
Description:
StandardEvent Notification:Raised when an event with no
associated resource is detected into the swnr platform

Name: ulcmNsResourceEvent
Description:
ResourceEvent Notification:Raised when an event with an
associated resource is detected into the swnr platform

Name: ulcmNsShutdown
Description:
Shutdown Notification:Raised when an swnr platform shutdown
is detected

Name: ulcmNsActiveAgentChange
Description:
ActiveAgentChange Notification:Raised when the SNMP agent is
designed as 'active' by TAP

Name: ulcmNsAlarmActive
Description:
AlarmActive Notification:Raised when a new alarm is created into
the AlarmActiveTable

Name: ulcmNsAlarmClear
Description:
AlarmActive Notification:Raised when a previously created alarm
is deleted from AlarmActiveTable
